    <briefdescription>
<para>Type trait to remove reference qualifiers from a type. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Removes both lvalue and rvalue reference qualifiers from a type, returning the underlying unqualified type.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Type</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The type to process</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
@SINCE_2_5.11</para>
